						Ignore Case? Class Default
				Description:
				Derived From
					Class: clsColumnGeneral
					Class: cfCachePool
				Class Variables
				Instance Variables
					!
					Boolean: ibInitialized
					String: isKey
					String: __sTemp
				Functions
					Function: AddRow
						Description:
						Returns
						Parameters
							String: s1
						Static Variables
						Local variables
						Actions
							Call SalListAdd( MyValue, s1)
					Function: SetKey
						Description:
						Returns
						Parameters
							String: sKey
						Static Variables
						Local variables
						Actions
							Set isKey = sKey
					Function: SetCacheElement
						Description: This function is for setting a hidden cache drop down which has the key elements of the 
								associated displayed cache field ie have 2 droplistcache fields on a form - one is descriptions 
								which is displayed, the other are keys of descriptions which are hidden - when the user
								selects a new description we want the hidden to be reset to the correct key also - on 
								SetCacheElement - if ibInitialized = FALSE then send a SAM_Dropdown to populate the 
								key cache field
						Returns
							Boolean:
						Parameters
							Number: nIndex
						Static Variables
						Local variables
						Actions
							If ibInitialized = FALSE
								! Call SalSendMsg( hWndItem, SAM_DropDown, 0, 0 )
								Call clsColDropListCache.Populate( isKey )
								Set ibInitialized = TRUE
							Call SalListSetSelect( hWndItem, nIndex )
				List Values
				Message Actions
					On SAM_Create
						Set ibInitialized = FALSE
					On SAM_DropDown
						If NOT ibInitialized
							Call clsColDropListCache.Populate( isKey )
							Set ibInitialized = TRUE
					On PAM_clsDF_CLEAR
						Set ibInitialized = FALSE
						Call SalListClear( hWndItem )
					On PAM_clsTBLCOL_RESET
						Call SetCacheElement( wParam )
						Call SalListQueryText( hWndItem, wParam, __sTemp )
						Call SalSetWindowText( hWndItem, __sTemp )
