				Class ChildKey: 0
				Class:
				Property Template:
				Class DLL Name:
				Title:
				Visible? Yes
				Editable? Yes
				Maximum Data Length: Default
				Data Type: String
				Justify: Left
				Width:  Default
				Width Editable? Yes
